{
  "texts": [
    "Here, h is the hidden state from the encoder layers h = encoder(u), and u is the input text or utterance.",
    "Decoder-Only ModelThe decoder-only architecture selected for this work is LLaMA2 [8].",
    "There are 3 sizes of LLaMA2: 7 billion, 13 billion, and 70 billion parameters.",
    "The version of choice is the 7 billion one.",
    "LLaMA2 is a generative model, and unlike the encoderonly models, it does not output a hidden state."
  ]
}